hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: magic story very thanks stylpharma.cz Lady Gaga may be the queen of outlandish fashion (meat dress anyone?) but sometimes she bestows a look on us that we think we might just actually be able to rock. Take this plaid shirt dress from Saint Laurent's Fall 2013 collection. Sometimes, if you wish hard enough, the fashion gods will bestow upon you a stylish trend that looks great and is highly wearable. Here we see one of those rare timeless pieces; the classic checked shirt. A wardrobe staple that has been worn by everyone from Kurt Kobain to Johnny Depp, the trusty piece nails the glam grunge trend.
